<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“菲奥娜，你弹得太好了。” 卡拉巴斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你太出色了!”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲奥娜哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我经常练习。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把吉他递给卡拉巴斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“弹给我听听吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯轻轻地弹了弹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王在菲奥娜耳边小声说：“卡拉巴斯会成为一个好丈夫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很有钱，拥有很多地。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲奥娜耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只想要一个善良的丈夫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯走上山坡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他敲了敲城堡的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个年轻人开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想见见食人魔。” 普斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“食人魔出去了。” 年轻人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以进来等他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>年轻人带普斯走进一个房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请坐。” 他说，“请随意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>年轻人叫来一位仆人。“拿茶来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，好的！” 仆人赶紧去拿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很快就回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他倒茶的时候双手不停颤抖着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“仆人为什么这么紧张？” 普斯想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>周围站着其他仆人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看上去也都很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……” 普斯想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我也变紧张了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 普斯对年轻人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我该走了。我得……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>年轻人突然变得又大又绿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的脸变丑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯吓了一跳。“你就是食人魔！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>